casebody.data:
October 19, 1959. No. 1,

October Term, 1957.

United States v. Shotwell Manufacturing Co. et al. George B. Christensen for Shotwell Manufacturing Co. et al., and William T. Kirby . for Sullivan, movants. Solicitor General Rankin for the United States in opposition. [See 355 U. S. 233, 352 U. S. 997.]

The motion for leave to file motions to vacate orders of December 16, 1957, granting certiorari etc. and for other relief is denied.
